In [13]:
def rename_mitype(mitype):
    if 'Vantage Pro' in mitype:
        return 'Davis'
    elif 'WXT' in mitype:
        return 'Vaisala'
    elif 'PWS' in mitype:
        return 'ICB'
    elif 'WS-UMB' in mitype:
        return 'Lufft'
    elif 'M-49M' in mitype:
        return ''
    elif '-1' in mitype:
        return '-1'
    elif any(item in mitype for item in ['', '', '', '', '', '']):
        return '-94'
    return mitype
